<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - SMS</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Student Management System</h1>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    The Student Management System (SMS) is a comprehensive platform designed to streamline the management
                    of student records and academic documents.
                </p>
                
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">Our Features</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Easy access to registration cards and result cards</li>
                    <li>Secure document storage and retrieval</li>
                    <li>Simple search functionality using registration and roll numbers</li>
                    <li>Administrative dashboard for managing student records</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">How It Works</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Students can easily search for their academic documents using their registration number and roll number.
                    The system provides instant access to registration cards and result cards in PDF format.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>